NAME

DateTime::Locale::fur - Locale data examples for the Friulian (fur) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Friulian locale.

  martars

Date Formats

Full

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = martars 5 di Fevrâr dal 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = vinars 22 di Dicembar dal 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = sabide 15 di Setembar dal -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 di Fevrâr dal 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 di Dicembar dal 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 di Setembar dal -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05/02/2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22/12/1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/09/-10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05/02/08
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22/12/95
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/09/-10

Available Formats

Bh (h B)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 6 B
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9 B
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4 B

Bhm (h:mm B)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 6:30 B
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9:05 B
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4:44 B

Bhms (h:mm:ss B)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 6:30:30 B
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9:05:02 B
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4:44:23 B

E (ccc)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = mar
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = vin
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = sab

EBhm (E h:mm B)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = mar 6:30 B
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = vin 9:05 B
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = sab 4:44 B

EBhms (E h:mm:ss B)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = mar 6:30:30 B
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = vin 9:05:02 B
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = sab 4:44:23 B

EHm (E HH:mm)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = mar 18:30
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = vin 09:05
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = sab 04:44

EHms (E HH:mm:ss)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = mar 18:30:30
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = vin 09:05:02
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = sab 04:44:23

Ed (d E)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 mar
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 vin
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 sab

Ehm (E h:mm a)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = mar 6:30 p.
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = vin 9:05 a.
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = sab 4:44 a.

Ehms (E h:mm:ss a)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = mar 6:30:30 p.
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = vin 9:05:02 a.
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = sab 4:44:23 a.

Gy (G y)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = ddC 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = ddC 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = pdC -10

GyMMM (G y MMM)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = ddC 2008 Fev
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = ddC 1995 Dic
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = pdC -10 Set

GyMMMEd (G y MMM d, E)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = ddC 2008 Fev 5, mar
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = ddC 1995 Dic 22, vin
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = pdC -10 Set 15, sab

GyMMMd (G y MMM d)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = ddC 2008 Fev 5
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = ddC 1995 Dic 22
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = pdC -10 Set 15

H (HH)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 18
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 09
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 04

Hm (H:mm)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 18:30
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9:05
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4:44

Hms (HH:mm:ss)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 18:30:30
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 09:05:02
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 04:44:23

Hmsv (HH:mm:ss v)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 18:30:30 UTC
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 09:05:02 UTC
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 04:44:23 UTC

Hmv (HH:mm v)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 18:30 UTC
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 09:05 UTC
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 04:44 UTC

M (L)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 12
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 9

MEd (E d/M)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = mar 5/2
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = vin 22/12
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = sab 15/9

MMM (LLL)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = Fev
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Dic
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Set

MMMEd (E d MMM)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = mar 5 Fev
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = vin 22 Dic
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = sab 15 Set

MMMMEd (E d MMMM)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = mar 5 Fevrâr
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = vin 22 Dicembar
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = sab 15 Setembar

MMMMW-count-other ('week' W 'of' MMMM)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = week 1 of Fevrâr
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = week 3 of Dicembar
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = week 2 of Setembar

MMMMd (d 'di' MMMM)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 di Fevrâr
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 di Dicembar
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 di Setembar

MMMd (d MMM)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Fev
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Dic
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Set

MMd (d/MM)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5/02
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22/12
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/09

Md (d/M)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5/2
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22/12
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/9

d (d)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15

h (h a)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 6 p.
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9 a.
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4 a.

hm (h:mm a)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 6:30 p.
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9:05 a.
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4:44 a.

hms (h:mm:ss a)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 6:30:30 p.
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9:05:02 a.
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4:44:23 a.

hmsv (h:mm:ss a v)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 6:30:30 p. UTC
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9:05:02 a. UTC
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4:44:23 a. UTC

hmv (h:mm a v)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 6:30 p. UTC
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9:05 a. UTC
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4:44 a. UTC

ms (mm:ss)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 30:30
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 05:02
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 44:23

y (y)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10

yM (M/y)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2/2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 12/1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 9/-10

yMEd (E, d/M/y)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = mar, 5/2/2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = vin, 22/12/1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = sab, 15/9/-10

yMMM (MMM y)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = Fev 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Dic 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Set -10

yMMMEd (E d MMM y)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = mar 5 Fev 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = vin 22 Dic 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = sab 15 Set -10

yMMMM (LLLL 'dal' y)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = Fevrâr dal 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Dicembar dal 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Setembar dal -10

yMMMd (y MMM d)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008 Fev 5
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995 Dic 22
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10 Set 15

yMd (y-MM-dd)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008-02-05
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995-12-22
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10-09-15

yQQQ (QQQ y)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = T1 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = T4 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = T3 -10

yQQQQ (QQQQ y)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = Prin trimestri 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Cuart trimestri 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Tierç trimestri -10

yw-count-other ('week' w 'of' Y)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = week 6 of 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = week 51 of 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = week 37 of -10
